HEADWORD: Pestiduct
<hw>Pes"ti*duct</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pestis</ets> pest + <ets>ductus</ets> a leading, fr.
<ets>ducere</ets> to lead.]</ety> <def>That which conveys contagion or
infection.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Donne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
